{"tid":899643,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【改詞MV】送別李斯特城老闆 - 維猜","createTime":"2018-11-12T15:18:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-16T13:28:03.000Z","uid":37464,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fa92269c22c0fbc876cd2bd1e799cf6959e5cad7","tid":899643,"uid":37464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T15:18:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://youtu.be/l9XYkJRvM5Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fl9XYkJRvM5Y&d=hSlaLJfYDtgp23%2BnQkQNqZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=0676a0b3\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/l9XYkJRvM5Y</a><br />\n<br />\n作曲：王雙駿 <br />\n原詞：林夕 <br />\n填詞：DC_ <br />\n演唱：Rider. <br />\n<br />\n生　生於某國土　家當也豐厚 <br />\n憑甚麼因由　為異鄉擔憂 <br />\n球會　多得你駐守　至踏進軌道 <br />\n當日種種演說　竟一一看到 <br />\n<br />\n故事如童話般　際遇如流水般 <br />\n留下夢幻電影　演出過程　仍動魄心驚 <br />\n剪輯裡留縮影　獎杯裡留有蹤影 <br />\n藏入了記憶　不需說明 <br />\n這一趟路程　已經心領 <br />\n<br />\n想　當天你構想　都已算擁有 <br />\n成就的背後　是大家聚頭 <br />\n維猜　始終對每位　以善意招待 <br />\n不願看著淚流　陪各界分憂<br />\n <br />\n故事如童話般　際遇如流水般 <br />\n從未被預炓　高低的旅程　才是個經典 <br />\n聽著誰人反映　勝利時仍會清醒 <br />\n才讓這市區　不需轉型　已足夠盡興　時代做證 <br />\n<br />\n感謝永遠你都傾心的奉獻　 故事未落幕　<br />\n承繼過來　從你往昔伸展 <br />\n<br />\n終於你能休息　當天你留低的 <br />\n傳誦後代萬世　衝開困壁　讓藍狐在最耀眼的 <br />\n多得你　當天收購做救星 <br />\n懷念你那天　揮手那時　捧杯那路程　笑得高興"},{"pid":"3dc2582ccc4a3e6964048ade19abbf5abf6547bf","tid":899643,"uid":18276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T15:19:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93d1a5ba9a5b0c219416b03b0af58307b5e8fab2","tid":899643,"uid":17522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T15:21:14.000Z","msg":"Support<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a0a6b8e90486b3dca73ace79007e3706dae6396","tid":899643,"uid":37464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T17:12:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://youtu.be/pW9BNbazgK8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpW9BNbazgK8